  "original_title": "\u0da0\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd3 \u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db6\u0dbd \u0db7\u0dd6 \u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca\u0db4\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dd1\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Strong earthquake hits Chile",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the European Mediterranean Seismological Center (EMSC), a magnitude 6.2 earthquake has hit Antofagasta, Chile.",
        "The center indicated that the earthquake occurred at a depth of 80 km.",
        "However, no information has been reported so far regarding the loss of life or property due to this earthquake."
      ],
